oisy. Plus, the keyboard and mouse combo comes with a separate calculator numeric keypad and multi-media hot keys for quick access to your music, internet, email, and more.\nThis wireless keyboard and mouse set offers a slim and compact design that's perfect for any workspace. It includes a full-size QWERTY keyboard and a wireless compact mouse with a separate calculator numeric keypad and three adjustable DPI levels (800-1200-1600). The sweat-resistant, skin-friendly finish mouse in contoured shape would provide hours of work comfortably. Additionally, the keyboard and mouse combo takes adaptability, material, and craftsmanship into consideration. The keyboard has a slope angle for the great typing position, ensuring that you'll be able to type efficiently without straining your wrists.\nOverall, if you're looking for a high precision and ergonomic wireless keyboard and mouse combo that's both reliable and affordable, the Cimetech 2.4G Ultra-Thin Keyboard and Mouse Set is definitely worth checking out. Its wide compatibility with various operating systems ensures that it will work well with most computers and laptops. So why wait? Upgrade your workspace today with the Cimetech 2.4G Ultra-Thin Keyboard and Mouse Set!", ": \n# LYCANDER Gaming Keyboard UK Review\nAs a gamer, I know how important it is to have a reliable and responsive keyboard when playing games. That's why I was thrilled to try out the LYCANDER Gaming Keyboard UK. With its 19 anti-ghosting keys, 1.8m cable, and rainbow backlight, this keyboard is perfect for anyone looking to upgrade their gaming setup.\n## Pros\nFirstly, one of the most impressive features of this keyboard is its anti-ghosting technology. This means that no matter how many keys you press simultaneously, they all register correctly. This is especially useful during fast-paced gameplay where every second counts. Additionally, the rainbow backlight creates a fun and vibrant gaming environment, which is sure to impress your friends. The